Glacier Vault lock
adopt a worm model
create a vault lock policy
lock the policy for future edits
helpful for compliance and data retention
------------------------
S3 Object lock

adopt a worm model
block an object version deletion for a specific amount of time
retention mode compliance
  object versions cant be overwritten or deleted from any user, including root user
  object retention modes cant be changed, and retention periods cant be shortened
retention mode governance
  most users cant overwrite or delete an object version or alter its lock settings
  some users have special permissions to change the retention or delete the object
retention period: protect the object for a fixed period, it can be extended
Legal hold
  protects the object indefinitely, independent from retention period
  can be freely placed and removed using the s3:PutObjectLegalHold IAM Permssions

